description: "Complete federal retirement preparation checklist. Timeline from 5 years out to retirement day covering FERS, TSP, FEHB, FEGLI, and all essential federal employee retirement steps."
serviceTag: "federal"
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
